@startuml
title State Management Lifecycle

Idle    --> Loading : *Fetch() called (Main mounts)
Loading --> Loaded  : API resolves\n(state normalized by id)
Loading --> Error   : API rejects

Loaded  --> Loaded  : re-render / re-mount\n(guard: if (loaded) return)
Loaded  --> Loaded  : transactions only:\nSSE -> upsert / delete

Error   --> Loading : *Fetch() retried\n(loaded stays false)
@enduml
